function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorDamaged) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idThisQuest) then
		if Hydra.ActorDistanceBetweenActors(idActorDamaged,idThisQuest) <= 12 then Hydra.EventSendToActor("EnableSpawning",idThisQuest,idThisQuest) end
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	
	for i=1, #tSpawns do
		if not Hydra.ActorIsValid(tSpawns[i]) or not Hydra.ActorIsAlive(tSpawns[i]) then
			table.remove(tSpawns,i)
		end
	end
	
	table.insert(tSpawns,idActorSpawned)
	
	local idRunTo = tRunToLocs[Hydra.GetRandomInt(1,#tRunToLocs)]
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActorSpawned,idRunTo, "NPC_RUN", false)
	
	Hydra.ActorSetRetreatRadius(idActorSpawned,100)
	Hydra.ActorClearAITether(idActorSpawned)
	Hydra.ActorAddAITarget(idActorSpawned, idRunTo, true)
--	Hydra.ActorSetAITether(idActorSpawned, idRunTo)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("ShouldIPlayVO",idThisQuest,ParentController)

end
